    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://duncanm14.github.io/project2-docs/api/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://duncanm14.github.io/project2-docs/api/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;api-endpoints-laravel-12--sanctum-authentication&#34;&gt;API Endpoints (Laravel 12 + Sanctum Authentication)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your API uses Laravel Sanctum for token-based authentication.&lt;br&gt;
Users authenticate with &lt;code&gt;/api/users/login&lt;/code&gt; to receive a Bearer token, which must be included in all protected requests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Authorization header format:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;authentication&#34;&gt;Authentication&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;post-apiuserslogin&#34;&gt;POST /api/users/login&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Authenticates a user and returns a Sanctum API token.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;request-body&#34;&gt;Request Body&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;username&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;demo&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;password&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;password123&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;response&#34;&gt;Response&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-json&#34; data-lang=&#34;json&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;{
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;token&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;5|xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;get-apiusersme&#34;&gt;GET /api/users/me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protected route. Returns the currently authenticated user.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
